+## 2026-05-22 — Clarification session (Q1–Q8)
+
+Running `/plan-2-v2-clarify` adapted to pre-spec state: answers logged here; downstream `/plan-1b-v2-specify` picks them up.
+
+### Q1: Workflow Mode
+
+**Answer**: **Simple Mode**.
+
+**Implications** (per plan-2-v2-clarify skill):
